.TH "sys_get_robust_list" 9 "sys_get_robust_list" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
sys_get_robust_list \- Get the robust-futex list head of a task
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "long" sys_get_robust_list
.BI "(int pid "  ","
.BI "struct robust_list_head __user * __user * head_ptr "  ","
.BI "size_t __user * len_ptr "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "pid" 12
pid of the process [zero for current task]
.IP "head_ptr" 12
pointer to a list-head pointer, the kernel fills it in
.IP "len_ptr" 12
pointer to a length field, the kernel fills in the header size
